  "time_ut": 1656262223,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dc5\u0db9 \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc4\u0dcf \u0d85\u0db1\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dca \u0db1\u0d9c\u0dbb\u0db6\u0daf \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0da9\u0dd4 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Holidays for Colombo schools and other urban schools",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Following discussions with Provincial Secretaries of Education, Provincial Directors of Education and Principals of Urban National Schools, the Ministry of Education issued a press release on June 25, 2022 regarding the conduct of schools during the week from 27 June to 01 July 2022.",
        "However, the Ministry of Education says that there is a problem regarding the running of schools during the week from June 27 to July 01, 2022 as the Ministry of Power and Energy has informed that the distribution of fuel in the island will not be possible during the week starting from June 27, 2022.",
        "Therefore, it has been decided not to hold schools in the Colombo region of the Western Province and nearby towns and schools in the main cities of other provinces during the week from 27th June to 1st July 2022 as in the previous week.",
        "Students and teachers will be notified to hold schools on Tuesdays, Wednesdays and Thursdays if they do not have transportation difficulties, as was the case last week in rural schools from June 27 to July 1, 2022. Teachers who do not attend school on these days due to transportation difficulties are also advised not to register as private holidays.",
        "However, if there is any problem regarding the running of schools during that week, the Provincial Secretaries of Education and the Provincial Directors of Education will inform the Provincial Governors and inform them to act accordingly.",
        "If term examinations are scheduled to be held for the GCE Advanced Level during the week beginning June 27, 2022, action will be taken to conduct those term examinations two weeks later."
      ],
